\id 1TI - Borna New Testamnet
\h 1 T'imotiwos
\toc2 1 T'imotiwos
\toc1 1 T'imotiwos Maants
\toc3 1 T'im.
\mt3 Wosheetso P'awlos Shints Wosho
\mt1 T'imotiwos Maants
\imt1 Kindo
\ip T'imotiwosi eteets jawets na'o krstiyano Esiyi datsatse b́teshor, induwereron Ayhudi datsi asha, niho weeronmó Grik dats asha b́tesh, P'awlossh karntso b́ tohonat doo shishi finoshowere karnon bish tep'foni b́ tesh, P'awlos T'imotiwossh b́ guut'ts wosho shintso keez keewu een eenuwotsatsa b́ kitsir.
\ip Jamoniyere shino b́woshotse b́daniyruwo Ik'i mootse tuut teshts kooti danatse boatso bokotetuwok'owa b́tesh, ib wotts danman b́ bado ayhudiwotska, b́ badonmó k'osh naari ashuwots hasabiyo b́ gitsotse detsts wotat, «Be'eyiru datsan morron baad'ewutsk b́ wottsotse kasho daatso falet k'osh wotts weeron ááshts danonat ik ik naari mishuwtsnat de'eyatse bíats kotonee» eti asaabiyatse te'eeka b́ tesh. Manats dabt b́ woshotse Ik'i maa k'eezi jangonat Ik' mangiy jangosh nemona, aani Ik'i maa jishiruwotsnat boon teú'awots detset boon geyit amalo kitsituwoniye. B́ s'uwaatsnowere T'imotiwos Iyesus Krstosko doo guutso awuk'o wottso bín b́ geyituwok'onat b́ beyiru ay ashuwotsoke bín s'iilit keewotse aatewotse P'awlos bísh b́ iztso datsituwone.
\iot Jamon mas'aafan b́detstso
\io1 B tuwo 1:1-2
\io1 Ik' moonat b́ guutsuwots jango 1:3—3:16
\io1 T'imotiwossh b́ fini jangosh imets dano 4:1—6:21
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ik'o no atoke no nojangtso Iyesus Krstos tzaziyon woshek wottso P'awlosoke.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Wosh. 16:1\x* Imnetiyon ari t naayi wottso T'imotiyossh, Ik'o nonihokere, nodoonz Iyesus Krstosoke s'aatonat mihretiyonu, jenonu neesh wotowe.
\s1 Kooti danatse boatso bokotetuwok'o b́ k'altsok'o
\p 
\v 3 Mek'edoniy maants tiamor neesh oona ti ettsok'on, manoke fa'a ash ik ikuwots kooti dano bodanirawok'o nwoshish Efesonitse beewe.
\v 4 Tururonat s'uu deshaw naar taawo maants k'ayr boanerawok'o boon azazowe, keewanots moosha bodoweti bako amanon fineyiru Ik'i finosh t'ak'ameratsnee.
\v 5 Tzaziyanmó nib s'ayinotse, asaabi s'ayinon, arik wotts amanon daatsets shunoniye.
\v 6 Ik ik ashuwots keewanotsatse k'aleyat k'awunts deshaw moosho maants k'az anernee.
\v 7 Man bok'aluwere nemo daniyruwotsi woto geeyatniye, wotowabako bokeewiruwo danatsne, arkeewetsnone boetirwono t'iwintsratsne.
\p 
\v 8 Asho geyitsok'on bín b́finiyal nemo sheeng b́wottsok'o danfone.
\v 9 Mank'owa nemo ned'iye ash kááwuwots b́woterawk'o danfone, nemo beeze mishetswotsnat k'uur finetsuwotsshe, Ik'osh k'erawwotsnat morr finetsuwotsshe, s'ayin woterawwotsnat kash keewo gac'iruwotsshe, bonihonat bo indon úd'iru kash úd'iruwots,
\v 10 Widetswotsna, g'ad'wotsnat, asho up'dek'amt kemiru jaktswotsnat kootetswotsi, kooton taarirwotsnat arik wotts dano k'uriru keew jamo finiruwotsshe.
\v 11 Arik wotts danonmó b́ daatset mangiyets Ik'o b́ shishits mangts doo shishiyone, doo shishiyanwere taash adar imetsoniyee.
\s1 P'awlos Ik'o oorowe eti jangosh b́t'intsts udo
\p 
\v 12 Finosh taan amanetso woshde naashiyosh taawdek't imtso nodoonz Iyesus Krstosi udirwe.
\v 13 Dab haniyere shin Krstosi c'ashtsonat gishtso, ketitso twotiyalor, bí taash mhretiyo b́woshi, bíwere taash mhretiyan b́wosh taa jaman t k'al daronat aman tk'aztsatse tuutson b́ teshtsotsne.
\v 14 Noo Ik'o s'aato Iyesus Krstosn nok wotts imnetiyonat t shunonton s'eent ooytso taash imere.
\v 15 «Iyesus Krstos morr finetswotsi kashiwosh datsats waare» etiru aap'o arikonat ash jamo dek'o bin b́ geyit keewe, morrets jamuwotsitsnor bítsi bog morretso taane.
\v 16 Ernmó taash mihretiyow oshere, taash mhretiyo woshere Iyesus Krstos ayidek't ayts b́ k'amoon ashe dash morretso wottsosh tiatse kitsosh bín amanitsuwotsnat dúre dúri kash datsituwotssh sheeng artso t wotishee.
\v 17 Mansh dúre dúri Nugúsosh, k'irrawosh, be'erawosh, Ik'o Izar Izewersh mangonat udon bísh dúre dúrosh wotowe! Amen.
\p 
\v 18 T naayi T'imotiwoso! haniyere shin njangosh bek'on keewetsok'on azazets adaranotsi neesh imetuwe, bek'mann jisheyar kes'i sheengo kec'ee,
\v 19 Amanonat maac' s'ayinetso wotowe, ash ik ikuwots bonibo bojuutsatse tuutson markabo jongon b́t'ffok'o bo imnetiyo t'afs'uure.
\v 20 Boyitse Hemenewosnat t Iskndrn fa'enee, boowere Ik' c'ash aap'o keewo k'azo bo danetwok'o Shed'anosh beshidek'at imik'rere.
\c 2
\s1 Ik' mootsi Ik' k'ono
\p 
\v 1 Jamoniyere shino Ik'o ik'iyonat mangon s'eents beyi k'onon, sagadon, koshuwotssh Ik' k'ononat udona ash jamosh k'aletwok'owe ti iziri.
\v 2 Ik' shatonat sheeng amalon jisheyar jeenonat s'k err no beetwok'o jamotsere nugúsuwotsnat een een dats k'eeziru naash jamwotssh Ik'o k'onwere.
\v 3 Hanuwere noon kashitso Ik'o shinatse shengwonat bín geneúshit keewe.
\v 4 Ik' shuno ash jamwots kasharr aronowere bo danetwok'owe.
\v 5 Ik'o ike, dagotse wotde'e Ik'onat ashon manituwonu ike, bíwere ash wottso Iyesus Krstosiye.
\v 6 Ash jamo morrotse kishosh b́ tooko beshidek't imtso bíne, hanuwere aron bí aaw man b́ bodor Ik'o kashiy fino noosh kitsit gawoniye.
\v 7 Taa imnetiyonat aron doo shishiyosh wosheetsonat danifon wotat Ik' danaw ashuwotsok t woshe man jangoshe, han tietor ara tkeewiri bako kooratse.
\p 
\v 8 Eshe b́ be beyoke fa'a nungshwots fayonat shit'on k'ayr bo kishi s'aynman dambaan k'aúde Ik'o bo k'onitwok'owe t geyiri.
\v 9 Máátswotswere took s'iir wozewon wee awnts wee ink'uwon wee shawu gizon keewets tahon baatso b́woterawo jiitsonat botoko dashan detson wotts ash na'i taho tahde'ene.
\v 10 Ik'o mangiyirwone etts máátswots k'alo boosh b́ geyit sheeng finon baatsunee.
\v 11 Máátsu s'ik etonat azazewo daniye.
\v 12 Máátsu nungusho b daniyituwok'o wee nungushatse bialituwok'owa eraatse, biye s'ik eto bish geyife.
\v 13 Shino azeetso Adamiye, ilowere azetsu Hewaniyee.
\v 14 Ando ant'elcetsunat Ik'i nemo gaktsunu máátsuni bako ant'elcetso Adamiyaliye.
\v 15 Ernmó máátsu amanonat shunon s'ayinonowere kup'arr biatso koton bbetkawotyal na'a shuwon kashituwaniye.
\c 3
\s1 Ep'is k'op'isiwotsi
\p 
\v 1 Ash iko ep'is k'op'isiyo\f + \fr 3:1 \fqa Ep'is k'op'isiyo: \ft Ik' ashuwotsi jishiruwoniye. \f* «woto b́ geyyale sheeng fine b́ tewni» etiru aap'o arikee
\v 2 Eshe Ep'is k'op'isi iko, bí atse k'efetuwo deshawo, mááts ik s'uzu dek'tso, bí angok'on betuwo, b́ took keewiruwo, teron finituwo, ib dek'etwo, daniyosh faltuwo,
\v 3 Másherawo, moosho shunawo, maac' nef wottso, fayetsi woterawo, giz shunawo,
\v 4 B́ took moowo k'ezdek'o falituwo, b́ nanauwots mangon bísh aleyirwotsi woto geyituwe.
\v 5 B́ took moo k'ezdek'o falatse wotiyal asho Ik' mootsi ashuwotsi ak'aldeniya k'eezo b́ faliti?
\v 6 Dayablos bog taana eton fugeyat bí ats angshetsok'o karnon amantso bí ats angsherawok'o Ep'is k'opisiyo wotk'aye.
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:2-7 \xt Tito 1:6-9\x* B́ shútso b́ t'afre Shed'ani kamboots kindr b́ dihirawok'o amaneraw ashuwotsoke sheeng shútso detstso woto bín geyiyituwe.
\s1 Diyak'oniyots jango
\p 
\v 8 Diyak'oniwotswere mank'o mangiyetswotsnat ik alberets wottsuwotsi, weyiniyon dutsets biro ay uyawwotsi, gizoshowere ayide'er k'awntirwotsi woto geyiratse,
\v 9 Ando imnetiy mist'iryo nib s'ayinon koto boosh geyituwe,
\v 10 Bowere shino fadewne, maniyakonowere boatse s'iilr eegonor bo atse datserawwotsi wotarr bodatseyal diyak'oni fino finone.
\v 11 Aaninuwere bomáátswotswor mangiyetswotsi, ash oonerawwotsi, bo angok'on beyirwotsi, jam keewon amanetswotsi woto boosh geyife.
\v 12 Diyak'oniwots botook tookosh mááts iku kenih woto boosh geyife, bo nana'onat bo maa asho sheengsh detsonat k'eezo boon geyfe.
\v 13 Diyak'oni fino sheengeshde finitwots een ma'aregiyo daatsitune, Iyesus Krstosn wotts imnetiyo ááwu shuk'on keewo falituee.
\p 
\v 14-15 Karn aawotse weetuwe tietalorni, daneraka wook'ayr t teshetkawotiyala dure duron beyiruwo Ik'o moonat aron k'ons'ets irok'o Ik'i mootse asho awuk'o k'alo bín b́ geyituwok'o n danetuwok'o neen jishituwo neesh guut'etuwe.
\v 16 Noo haymanoti mist'iriyo hake baka eterawok'on eene, bíwere Ik'o
\q1 «Ash wotat be'ere,
\q2 ar b́ wottsok'o shayiron b́dani,
\q2 Melakiwotssho b́ be'eyi
\q1 Ash jamosh nabere,
\q2 datsatsi ash jamo bín boamani,
\q2 mangon daro maantsan b́ dek'eyi» etke.
\c 4
\s1 Koot daniyo danifuwotse
\p 
\v 1 S'ayn shayironmo kishidek't hank'o bí eti, «Dúr s'uwatsere ik ik ashuwots shelit shairwootsnat fo'erawwots danits dani jafrats sha'ar bo haymanotiyo haalitwune.»
\v 2 Han naari danan b́ t'up'ir bo ats danawwotsoknee, koto bokeworo biri k'ees'on mitsetsok'o wotat dungwtsts bo nibotse boosh shiyeraw ashuwotsokne.
\v 3 Hannk'o ashuwtswere de'ewo bo baziri, amantsuwotsnat ar dants ashuwots Ik'o mangifetsre bometuwok'o Ik'o boosh bí imts misho «Maak'ayere» ett bo baziyiri.
\v 4 Ik' azts jamo sheenge, udon deek'etkaa wotiyal eegoru juwet keewo aaliye.
\v 5 Ik' aap'onat Ik' k'onon s'aynk wotituwe.
\s1 Krstossh sheeng guutso woti jango
\p 
\v 6 Daniyan amantsuwotssh n danetka wotiyal imnetiyi aap'onat b́ shuuts n shairu sheeng danman danfetsat eentso, Iyesus Krstossh guuts sheengo wotitune.
\v 7 Ik' mangiyo bíyitse aalts datsanatsi turur keewatse wokowe Ik' ik'iyosh n tooko daniwe.
\v 8 Nmets atson n atso kup'iyosh ntook k'aniyo muk' keewoshe neesh b́ t'ak'amiti, ernmó Ik' mangiyosh ntooko k'aniyonmo andonat shino maantsi weet kashosh nojangiruwo b́ wottsosh jamosh noosh t'ak'amituwe.
\v 9 Eteets etanuwere ash jamo b́ dek'et arik wotts keewoniye.
\v 10 Noowere ash jamo kashituwon bítsnowere amants jamwotsi kashiti jamaawo beet Ik'on no jangirwosh finon no mawiri, nomak'oriri.
\p 
\v 11 Keewanotsno azazowe, daniwe,
\v 12 Jawets n wottsosh konuworu neen gac'k'aye, maniyere n keewon, n beyon, n shunon, n imnetiyonat s'ayn n woton amants jamwotssh sheengon ariyetso wotowe.
\v 13 Taa t wafetsosh s'ayn mas'aafwotsi ash ashuwotssh nababon, nabonat daniyon kup'owe.
\v 14 Bek'on nesh keeweworat Ik' máá eenashuwots bokisho niats bogedori kash s'aynon neesh imets im man batk'aye.
\v 15 Eenfere niamok'o ash jamo b bek'etwok'o keewu jamanotsats kup'owe, keewu jamanotsi finats jitsr n jamon keewon boosh ime.
\v 16 N tokonat n daniru finonsh niatso korde'e, keewanotsatso kup'owe, hank'o k'alon n tokonat neen k'ebiruwotsi kashitune.
\c 5
\s1 T'oow máátswots jangosh izets izo
\p 
\v 1 Ash eeno nihok'o woshde izuwe bako fayk'aye, jawetsono eshuwotskok'owa,
\v 2 Gaawer máátsuwotsno indok'o woshde s'iile, baruwotsno mish mishuwotsk'o woshde s'aynon boon s'iile.
\p 
\v 3 Arikon bo keniho bo atse k'irts máátswotsi mangiwe
\v 4 B keniho bí'atse k'irts mááatsu nana'otsi wee b na'i na'o b detsal nana'a manots shino bo maa ashuwotssh k'alo b́ geyituwo k'alune, bo indonat nihon bo indowonat aboowonsh gusho aaniwosh kash weeron fin boon gyituwo danne, manuwere Ik' gene'ushit keewe.
\v 5 Bi aal beyiru t'owu mááts wottsu, b tewuno Ik'ats woshde t'uwe aawo Ik'o bin b́ tep'etuwok'o Ik' k'onon kup'arr betuwaniye.
\v 6 Datsanatsi gene'ú mec'ro shunts t'oow máátsunmó bihe need'on k'irkiye.
\v 7 Bo atse gondo daatseraniyere bo beetuewk'o dananotsi boosh daniwe.
\v 8 B́ took jaguwotssh, bítsnor bomeyitsi ashuwotsi gawrawo bí b́ imnetiyo k'azkee, dab́ amaneraw ashuwotsiyeror iki gondefe.
\p 
\v 9 Keez ub natoniyere dash wotts bkenih k'irts máátsu t'oowo máátsuwots shúúts guut'eyru mezgebiyats guut'k'aye, dabnwor ik kenihosh amts máátsu woto bin geytuwe.
\v 10 Dabrnu nana'uwotsi shengshde ditson, ib dek'on, s'aynwots tufo mashon, kic'tswotsi tepon sheeng fin jamo k'alosh sheeng fin jamo finosh kup'tsu woto bish geytuwe.
\p 
\v 11 Bo kenih k'irts máatswotsitse enasherafa'úwots bo mets tewuno boon da'a b́de'e, Krstossh bo detsts shuno b́shapre mááts amo bo geyituwotse boon t'owu máátsuwotsi mazgabets mazabiyats guut'k'aye.
\v 12 Máátsanots shin Krstossh bokindts taareo bogaktsotsnowere botokats angshe bodowiri.
\v 13 Ando aani final beyo bodaneti, finl be mec'ro b́ woteftsere ash maa moots gúrar asho bo oniti, ash keewots bo kiniditi, keewosh boon geyira keewo bokeewiti.
\v 14 Hanshowere enasheraw t'owu máátswots máátso amr na'o bo shuwitwok'o, bo moono shengshde bo k'ezituwok'o, izituwe, hank'on t'elato boshútso t'afiyosh weerindo datsatse.
\v 15 Haniyere shinoru bo kenihi k'irts t'owu mááts ik ikuwots imneti weratse tuut Shed'ani shuutso sha'erne.
\v 16 Amants mááts iku meyitsere bo kenihi k'irts máátsuwots fa'ane wotiyal Ik' meyitsi ashuwotssh kur bowoterawok'o bíwere boon teúwiye, hank'onowere Ik' moow eegoru boon tep'etu deshaw bokenihi k'irts t'owu máátsuwotsi tep'o falfane.
\p 
\v 17 Ik' mootsi fino sheengshdek't jishiruwotsi, dabnu nabonat daniyonmawiru een ashuwotssh git kish wotts mango boosh geyife,
\v 18 S'ayn mas'aafotse «Mááyo sirbiru minzi beero b́ no no tipk'aye,» mank'o «fintsosh damozo daats bísh geyiyfe» etre.
\v 19 Wee gito wee keez asho b́ gawiyala bako Ik' meyitsi ashuwotsi jishiru eenashats t'intseyiru s'aamiyo dek'k'aye.
\v 20 K'osh k'osh ashuwots boshatetwok'o morro finiru ashuwotsi ash jamwots shinatse giishowe.
\p 
\v 21 N finiru keew jamon iko ikoniyere n bogshrawo t iztsank'on jamo ik aawon ns'iletwok'o Ik'onat Iyesus Krstosn marat'ets melakiwots shinatse adaran neesh imre
\v 22 N kisho ashuwotsats gerde boosh k'onr naashiwosh kark'aye, k'osh ashuwots morro nkayerawok'o n tooko s'aynon kord'e.
\p 
\v 23 N maac' weeshonat jam aawo n shodiruwi jangosh múk'shde weyiniyon dutsets biro úyee bako haniye okoon aats mec'ro ushk'aye.
\p 
\v 24 Ik ik ashuwots mrro be'ek b́ woto shin angshoniye b́kitsiri, k'osh ashuwots morro b́ be'et ja'arniye.
\v 25 Sheeng fino jamoshe b́ be'eti, aashat beyirwonwor be'eraniyere ooreratse.
\c 6
\s1 Guutsuwotssh imets izo
\p 
\v 1 Ik' shútsonat b́ danits danon b́ c'asherawok'o guuts guuts jamwots bo doonzotsi mangiyo boosh b́ geyituwok'owo dande'ene.
\v 2 Bodoonzots amank wotts doonz detsts guuts jamwots Iyesus Krstosn bo eshuwotsi bo wottsotse boon gac'k'ayine, bo fin manatse oot' datsituwots bo doonz doonzuwots amantsonat shuneets eshuu bowottsosh baltsoniye bogshide' boosh finone. Neewere daniyonat izon neen b́geyit haniye.
\s1 Kot daniyonat arik wotts gaalon
\p 
\v 3 Arikon Ik' k'eyi jango daniru danmanton ik wottso no doonz Iyesus Krstos aap'oman k'azt k'osh dan danyiru asho b́ beyal,
\v 4 man kofangirwonat b́jamon danawoniye, wotowabako mooshonat wed'eyon bíatsots gond tewuno s'eenb́gutsi, man b́ dowetwere okoora, faya, c'asha, amank'aza,
\v 5 Botooko kimt arikeewo boyitse t'afts ashuwots bofinefo k'ut'eraw mooshoniye, hank'o ashuwotssh Ik'osh k'ewo gizdatsi malee bí arefoni.
\p 
\v 6 «T detstso taash bodfe» etiru ashosh Ik' ik'iyoash woto ay oot'o daatsituwe.
\v 7 Datsanats dek'nowaatso eegor aaliye, datsatsnowere eegoru de'e no amet keewo aaliye.
\v 8 No meetuwonat no tahituwon nodatsitkawotiyal noosh bodfe.
\v 9 Gaaletsi wotosh geyiruwotsmó fadewon dihitúne, ash ashuwotsi awaashituwonat t'afiytu k'awuntsdeshaw gond keewon ay tewuni kambon deshetunee.
\v 10 Han b́ wotitwonwere gizi shuno gond jamwotssh t'up' b́ wottsi jangoshe.
\s1 P'awlos T'imotiyossh bí imts izonat tzaziyon
\p 
\v 11 Ik' ashono! Neho jamanotsatse k'ayi woc'e, kááwon, Shayiri ash woton, imnetiyon, shunon, k'amonowere kup'ar, maac' nefon sha'owe.
\v 12 Imnetiyon sheeng kaaro kaarowe, neen b́ maantsan b́ s'eegor ay wotts gawuwots shinatse ar wotts gawo ni imtso dúre dúri kasho deshde'e.
\v 13 Jam keewon kash imiru Ik'onat P'ent'eniya eteets P'ilat'os shinatse sheeng amaneyon gawutso Iyesus Krstos shinatse neesh keewiruwe.
\v 14 Nodoonz Iyesus Krstos b́ be'efetsosh t tzaziyan n shelawo shúúts s'ayinon korde'e.
\v 15 Krstos be'ewonwere, deretsonat b́s'uz altso, naashuwotsatsi naasho, doonzuwotsatsi doonzo bí etts aawotse b́ wotiti,
\v 16 Bíwere bíyal k'irawoniye, konuworu bíyok t'inosh b́ falawu shanotse b́ beyiri, bínowere konuworu be'atse, konuworu bek'osh falatse, mangonat dúre dúr angon bísh wotowe, amen.
\p 
\v 17 Datsanatsi gaaletsuwots bognona bo erawok'o wee bogaal amanek woterawmanats bo te'erawok'o boon azazowe, mank'o bo tewunon noo nogene'uwituwok'o jam keewo bogshede'er noosh imetuwo Ik'o atsats b́wotituwok'o azazowe.
\v 18 Aaninuwere sheeng fino bofinituwok'o, sheeng finonowere gaaletsi bowotitwok'o, tewud doonat bodetstso kayiyosh k'andek'tswotsi bowotituwok'o azazowe.
\v 19 Mank'oon arik wotts kasho daatsosh s'ap'dek'k wotts gaalo weyiru duratse botokish kakudek'etunee.
\p 
\v 20 T'imotiwoso! adaron neesh imetso korde'e, dan woterawo «Dan» ariru koton ooshiyatse wokowe.
\v 21 Ik ikuwots mannaari dano detsfone ett boamants weeratse k'aztuurne.
\p Ik'i s'aatoniye itnton wotowe.
